Description: # pyexe
        
        Python package to execute commands on local and remote server.
        
        ### Installation
        
        ```
        pip install pyexe
        ```
        
        ### Uses
        
        #### Local
        
        ```
        from pyexe import Local
        
        lc= Local()
        lc.exe("git status")
        ```
        
        #### Remote
        
        ```
        from pyexe import Remote
        
        rm= Remote("1.1.1.1", "root", "password")
        rm.connect()
        rm.exe("ls")
        ```
        
